OL,6,FMarion Holmes had come on behalf of
OL,7,Fher late husband, Peter. In 2010, he
OL,8,Fwas convicted of false accounting
OL,9,Fafter shortfalls at his branch in
OL,10,FNewcastle. Peter died before his
OL,11,Fconviction could be overturned.
OL,13,FFor years the Post Office had made
OL,14,Fthem believe they were on their own.
OL,15,FBut it's because of what these women
OL,16,Flost that they eventually found each
OL,17,Fother.
