OL,6,FDeirdre Connolly was accused of
OL,7,Fstealing thousands from her Post
OL,8,FOffice branch in County Tyrone,
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FShe said: "If we tried to tell people
OL,12,Fwhat happened they didn't understand
OL,13,Fit until the drama came out."
OL,15,FIn that ITV drama, Mr Bates vs the
OL,16,FPost Office, former sub-postmasters
OL,17,Fand mistresses and their families saw
OL,18,Ftheir stories played out on TV.
