OL,6,FAmong them were Suzanne Bates, who
OL,7,Frecently married her long-term partner
OL,8,F` the famous Alan Bates, as well as Jo
OL,9,FHamilton and Jess Kaur.
OL,11,FThey all say the show changed
OL,12,Feverything ` and yet still hasn't
OL,13,Fchanged enough.
OL,15,FMany are yet to receive their full
OL,16,Ffinancial settlements.
