OL,3,C'Where is the justice?': Post Office
OL,4,Cvictims on compensation 'cruelty'
OL,6,FOne of those is Seema Misra. She was
OL,7,Fsent to prison after being wrongly
OL,8,Fconvicted of stealing #70,000 from her
OL,9,FPost Office in Surrey. She was eight
OL,10,Fweeks pregnant at the time.
OL,12,F"It's not like compensation - it's our
OL,13,Fown money we are asking for," she told
OL,14,Fme.
OL,16,FSuzanne Bates accused the government
OL,17,Fof "prolonging the cruelty".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
