OL,6,F"We'll sit round a table with you,"
OL,7,Fshe said. "We'll sort you out."
OL,9,FSue Knight told the group that she
OL,10,Ffeels embarrassed about the fact she
OL,11,Fhas had her financial redress, when
OL,12,Fothers in the group have not. "Until
OL,13,Fthey've all had it I don't feel I can
OL,14,Fcelebrate," she explained.
OL,16,FEven for those who have now had
OL,17,Fcriminal convictions quashed the pain
OL,18,Fis still palpable.
