OL,3,C'Where is the justice?': Post Office
OL,4,Cvictims on compensation 'cruelty'
OL,6,FSeema Misra's parents didn't live to
OL,7,Fsee her get her name cleared, and
OL,8,FMarion's husband Peter died before his
OL,9,Fown exoneration.
OL,11,F"It was bittersweet for me," she said.
OL,12,F"You just think, why couldn't it have
OL,13,Fbeen before he died?"
OL,15,FThese women now share with each other
OL,16,Fexperiences that some of them couldn't
OL,17,Ftalk about for years.
OL,19,FNot even to their own children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
