OL,6,FJess Kaur had a mental breakdown and
OL,7,Ftried to take her own life when she
OL,8,Fwas taken to court by the Post Office.
OL,10,F"We never really spoke about it," she
OL,11,Fsaid. "So (my kids) got to see what I
OL,12,Fwent through by watching the drama,
OL,13,Fwhich was quite emotional for
OL,14,Feverybody."
OL,16,FTracey told the group that, as a
OL,17,Fmother, she felt "really guilty"
OL,18,Fbecause she "didn't protect" her
OL,19,Fchildren from the Post Office.
